Coastie
Homonym Number:
Word Class:noun
Sense Number:2
Definition:a West Coast [South Island] resident or a person who comes from that area.
Origin:abbreviation
Register: informal
Register 2:
Domain:[none]
Region:[none]
See:
Pronunciation:
Notes: distinguished from a person from the East Coast of the North Island.
Citations
