Quote: .. Greymouth claims me as their own. I was born and bred there - grew up there. It's cool. The Coasties yell out, "Hey, Brendon's from Greymouth. He's one of us." It's nice to be able to claim it. I'm in love with the West Coast and it's an identity thing.
